{"tid":2035641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳彥霖案 死因庭下月24日以非公開形式作研訊前檢討","createTime":"2020-05-26T04:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T06:33:53.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c49f1dd34e701e429ba0927dc5784df756a89ebb","tid":2035641,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"曾參與反送中集會的15歲職訓局青年書院女生陳彥霖，去年9月底離奇赤裸浮屍海面，警方及後指死因無可疑。根據法庭文件，死因裁判庭將就案件作研訊前檢討，訂於下月24日、即端午節前夕進行，預計需時半天。惟當日聆訊將以非公開形式進行，除非是有適當利害關係的人士，否則不得出席聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n詳情： <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200526/RCCYT5QNWRSANG2DE2JPFWZKMQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200526%2FRCCYT5QNWRSANG2DE2JPFWZKMQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY2a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=2a0fe273\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200526%2FRCCYT5QNWRSANG2DE2JPFWZKMQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=8453683b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200526/RCCYT5QNWRSANG2DE2JPFWZKMQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"13b8523ad45e56f6073eac1399aa2aa762d7c470","tid":2035641,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"關於沈教授20點之我見<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2035226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2035226</a>"},{"pid":"7299b63b498a9b2daae354c8f06505ff8bdd9599","tid":2035641,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"點解會無咩人理😞"},{"pid":